</div> <div class="ctynt_object" data-object="text" style="width: 870px; height: 947px; top: 83px; left: 60px; z-index: 50;">
<p><a data-cke-saved-href="http://www.harcoboe.net/file/28CECC5EFC" href="http://www.harcoboe.net/file/28CECC5EFC"></a></p>
