<p><br></p>
<p><a data-cke-saved-href="http://www.harcoboe.net/file/28CECC5EFC" href="http://www.harcoboe.net/file/28CECC5EFC">Fall 2020 Dual Credit Course Registration</a> - </p>
<p>Please note that we will follow this schedule whether online learning or in our building.</p>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>Pending a release from social distancing restrictions</strong>, John Ebert will be hosting an ACT Math Prep Class on <strong>Sunday, June 7</strong>, in the BMS LGI, from 5:00 pm - 8:00 pm.  Students must register at <a data-cke-saved-href="https://nam01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.johnebertmathactprep.com%2F&amp;data=02%7C01%7Cagwebster%40k12.wv.us%7C04045c32edc7405c42d608d7e2edd4dd%7Ce019b04b330c467a8bae09fb17374d6a%7C0%7C0%7C637227383416021001&amp;sdata=J3%2BZS5eF5odGHwA%2FO7FWX2FAE3Lx54LWc26nPbFw0sw%3D&amp;reserved=0" href="https://nam01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.johnebertmathactprep.com%2F&amp;data=02%7C01%7Cagwebster%40k12.wv.us%7C04045c32edc7405c42d608d7e2edd4dd%7Ce019b04b330c467a8bae09fb17374d6a%7C0%7C0%7C637227383416021001&amp;sdata=J3%2BZS5eF5odGHwA%2FO7FWX2FAE3Lx54LWc26nPbFw0sw%3D&amp;reserved=0" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" title="Original URL: http://www.johnebertmathactprep.com/. Click or tap if you trust this link.">http://www.johnebertmathactprep.com</a> prior to attending this free course.</p>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>Pending a release from social distancing restrictions, </strong>the ACT will be given on <strong>June 13, 2020</strong>.  The registration deadline is May 8, with late fees accepted until May 22.  Students will need to register at <a data-cke-saved-href="https://nam01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.actstudent.org%2Fregist%2Fdates.html&amp;data=02%7C01%7Cagwebster%40k12.wv.us%7C04045c32edc7405c42d608d7e2edd4dd%7Ce019b04b330c467a8bae09fb17374d6a%7C0%7C0%7C637227383416021001&amp;sdata=y6AwsDMP8UG2%2FB6n3W83YrHz%2FteVJMu2SCMFZgjDHgI%3D&amp;reserved=0" href="https://nam01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.actstudent.org%2Fregist%2Fdates.html&amp;data=02%7C01%7Cagwebster%40k12.wv.us%7C04045c32edc7405c42d608d7e2edd4dd%7Ce019b04b330c467a8bae09fb17374d6a%7C0%7C0%7C637227383416021001&amp;sdata=y6AwsDMP8UG2%2FB6n3W83YrHz%2FteVJMu2SCMFZgjDHgI%3D&amp;reserved=0" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" title="Original URL: http://www.actstudent.org/regist/dates.html. Click or tap if you trust this link.">http://www.actstudent.org/regist/dates.html</a>.</p>
<p>All students wishing to enroll in dual credit college classes for the 2020-2021 school year, including current sophomores, are strongly encouraged to take the June 13th ACT to ensure timely registration for college classes starting in August.</p>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>Pending a release from social distancing restrictions, </strong>the ACT will be given on <strong>July 18, 2020</strong>.  The registration deadline is June 19, with late fees accepted until May 22.  Students will need to register at <a data-cke-saved-href="https://nam01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.actstudent.org%2Fregist%2Fdates.html&amp;data=02%7C01%7Cagwebster%40k12.wv.us%7C04045c32edc7405c42d608d7e2edd4dd%7Ce019b04b330c467a8bae09fb17374d6a%7C0%7C0%7C637227383416030996&amp;sdata=zkZXulevJCB5%2BjJjqNEoBJ5J2zCN5%2FhwWUPKkGDjfHo%3D&amp;reserved=0" href="https://nam01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.actstudent.org%2Fregist%2Fdates.html&amp;data=02%7C01%7Cagwebster%40k12.wv.us%7C04045c32edc7405c42d608d7e2edd4dd%7Ce019b04b330c467a8bae09fb17374d6a%7C0%7C0%7C637227383416030996&amp;sdata=zkZXulevJCB5%2BjJjqNEoBJ5J2zCN5%2FhwWUPKkGDjfHo%3D&amp;reserved=0" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" title="Original URL: http://www.actstudent.org/regist/dates.html. Click or tap if you trust this link.">http://www.actstudent.org/regist/dates.html</a>.</p>
